294
00:19:32,390 --> 00:19:34,030
He also said you liked me.

295
00:19:43,110 --> 00:19:44,110
But I know

296
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:45,630
it must be nonsense.

297
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:54,710
That's just silly.

298
00:19:58,910 --> 00:20:01,070
Is what he said true?

299
00:20:13,510 --> 00:20:15,670
Why don't you wait for me to go home after school today?

300
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:18,750
Power Jiao,

301
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:20,030
you've grown up.

302
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:21,430
Don't be a baby.

303
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:23,470
You're unhappy because of Anran again.

304
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,430
What is it again?

305
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:33,630
She's clearly just around the corner.

306
00:20:33,630 --> 00:20:36,310
Why do you have to travel far and wide looking for her?

307
00:20:38,990 --> 00:20:40,110
Travel far and wide?

308
00:20:40,790 --> 00:20:42,590
Is it popular to talk like a literary man these days?

309
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:46,310
Can't you get to the point?

310
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:47,750
I mean

311
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,910
since you like her and she likes him.

312
00:20:50,670 --> 00:20:51,790
You'd better...

313
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,390
If I didn't listen to you kids chatting,

314
00:20:58,470 --> 00:20:59,390
I wouldn't know

315
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:02,550
that my son here,

316
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:04,350
in the words of young people,

317
00:21:05,790 --> 00:21:06,870
is actually a back-up.

318
00:21:07,990 --> 00:21:09,070
Good evening, sir.

319
00:21:09,470 --> 00:21:10,080
Weijiao,

320
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:12,470
according to your talking,

321
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:13,710
it seems that

322
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:15,350
you're also a back-up.

323
00:21:18,150 --> 00:21:18,950
How ashamed!

324
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,270
Mom, I'm back.

325
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:25,150
Weijiao is really cute.

326
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:29,750
Little brat,

327
00:21:30,710 --> 00:21:33,230
why didn't you tell me earlier that you were a back-up?

328
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:34,950
I'd be nicer to you.

329
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:38,910
No wonder you look so sad every day.

330
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:44,230
What's that?

331
00:21:44,790 --> 00:21:46,230
Aren't you a back-up?

332
00:21:46,710 --> 00:21:48,150
How am I a back-up?

333
00:21:48,150 --> 00:21:48,950
You see,

334
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:50,190
you liked mom

335
00:21:50,230 --> 00:21:51,230
and mom liked another guy.

336
00:21:51,230 --> 00:21:53,230
So you're an old back-up.

337
00:21:54,990 --> 00:21:55,750
Back-up.

338
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:56,950
You back-up.

339
00:21:56,990 --> 00:21:58,150
You're a back-up.

340
00:21:58,150 --> 00:21:59,270
You're an old back-up.

341
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,150
Back-up son.

342
00:22:00,190 --> 00:22:01,950
You back-up dad.

343
00:22:02,470 --> 00:22:03,550
Ancestral back-up.

344
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,790
You passed it on to me.

345
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:05,950
You back-up.

346
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:07,350
What are you yelling about at night?

347
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:07,963
Stop yelling!

348
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:09,790
Two back-ups.

349
00:22:33,910 --> 00:22:34,510
Big Mouth,

350
00:22:34,870 --> 00:22:35,910
we arranged for them to meet yesterday.

351
00:22:35,910 --> 00:22:36,990
It was very effective.

352
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:39,590
You see, she is in a much better mood today.

353
00:22:41,550 --> 00:22:42,163
Big Mouth,

354
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:43,630
what's the plan next?

355
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:44,790
You have to make good arrangements.

356
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:46,070
Don't make it so tiring as yesterday.

357
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:48,190
The better I arrange it,

358
00:22:49,070 --> 00:22:51,110
the sooner she leaves you, right?

359
00:23:01,990 --> 00:23:02,830
Who am I?

360
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:04,150
I'm your brother Doggo.

361
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:05,230
Don't worry about me.

362
00:23:07,070 --> 00:23:07,680
Doggo.

363
00:23:09,630 --> 00:23:10,350
No matter what,

364
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:12,630
I still love you.

365
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:21,750
I love you too.

366
00:23:31,510 --> 00:23:34,630
No matter what, I still love you.

367
00:23:34,630 --> 00:23:35,710
It sounds great!

368
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:37,070
I will say this to Chen Yuanyuan.

369
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:37,990
Jot down again.

370
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:38,590
Pay me!

371
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:39,750
Go away!

372
00:24:03,230 --> 00:24:03,830
What's the matter?

373
00:24:08,910 --> 00:24:09,870
It's your birthday again?

374
00:24:10,230 --> 00:24:11,750
No, I brought you breakfast.

375
00:24:14,230 --> 00:24:14,830
Me?

376
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:17,350
All right, it's time for class.

377
00:24:17,630 --> 00:24:19,310
Did you have a good time with Wenqin yesterday?

378
00:24:19,550 --> 00:24:20,670
You look so happy today.

379
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,310
Have a taste.

380
00:24:32,046 --> 00:24:32,646
Is it sweet?

381
00:24:34,990 --> 00:24:35,596
Yeah.

382
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:38,230
Spicy noodles are more delicious.

383
00:24:40,630 --> 00:24:42,350
They are all delicious, alright?

384
00:24:56,063 --> 00:24:56,670
Wenqin.

385
00:24:56,710 --> 00:24:57,910
I heard that the police are investigating you.

386
00:24:57,950 --> 00:24:58,750
Why don't you hide away?

387
00:24:58,790 --> 00:24:59,590
Hide? My foot!

388
00:24:59,830 --> 00:25:00,990
What will be will be.

389
00:25:01,230 --> 00:25:02,350
Where can I hide?

390
00:25:02,746 --> 00:25:03,356
Wenqin.

391
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:08,310
Did you arrange it yesterday?

392
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:09,990
Come on, Wenqin.

393
00:25:12,190 --> 00:25:12,950
It looks fancy.

394
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:14,630
Anran asked me to bring it to you.

395
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,190
Take a look at it.

396
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,830
Who dug a hole?

397
00:25:23,430 --> 00:25:24,790
Perhaps.

398
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,590
I accidentally broke it on the way.

399
00:25:27,990 --> 00:25:28,596
Bro,

400
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:31,590
I really can't understand your behavior.

401
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:32,430
What do I do?

402
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:34,190
I behave very normally.

403
00:25:34,190 --> 00:25:35,630
Do you like her?

404
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,430
If you really like her,

405
00:25:36,430 --> 00:25:37,750
just go and get her.

406
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:39,030
Why do you always do this?

407
00:25:40,390 --> 00:25:41,510
Don't you like her?

408
00:25:42,470 --> 00:25:43,710
It's none of your business.

409
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:59,150
Why don't you help me?

410
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:02,470
We're brothers.

411
00:26:02,710 --> 00:26:03,590
How can I help you?

412
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:05,510
You can help me

413
00:26:05,790 --> 00:26:07,110
love her for my sake.

414
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,390
Are you out of your mind?

415
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:14,750
Don't be so rude.

416
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:17,230
There are some things you don't know.

417
00:26:18,150 --> 00:26:19,550
What could have happened to you?

418
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:22,310
You're just like me.

419
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:24,070
Too far away.

420
00:26:24,470 --> 00:26:25,430
We're too far away from her.

421
00:26:27,790 --> 00:26:29,270
How far away?

422
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:33,270
We're here

423
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:34,230
and she's over there.

424
00:26:34,430 --> 00:26:35,630
What do you mean?

425
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:36,710
She's over there.

426
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,270
Let's eat.

427
00:26:50,430 --> 00:26:51,310
Okay, okay.

428
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,590
Let's eat together.

429
00:26:57,630 --> 00:26:59,670
Anran, you're so good at buying food.

430
00:26:59,710 --> 00:27:00,750
It's such a balanced diet.

431
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:02,110
Doesn't it look delicious, Wenqin?

432
00:27:08,163 --> 00:27:08,763
Wenqin,

433
00:27:09,230 --> 00:27:10,990
this looks so delicious.

434
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,070
Eat quickly. I have something to do.

435
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:46,030
I've got to go.

436
00:27:49,430 --> 00:27:50,790
Then can I stay here

437
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,150
waiting for you to come back?

438
00:28:01,910 --> 00:28:03,190
Why don't I take you back to school first?

439
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:04,596
Okay.

440
00:28:06,190 --> 00:28:07,790
Then I'll enjoy myself.

441
00:28:07,790 --> 00:28:09,590
I'll have all the food.

442
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:37,680
Anran.

443
00:28:39,710 --> 00:28:40,550
Look!

444
00:28:41,550 --> 00:28:42,910
There weren't any houses before.

445
00:28:43,863 --> 00:28:44,463
Yeah.

446
00:28:44,910 --> 00:28:46,230
We've been here before.

447
00:28:46,430 --> 00:28:47,670
It's really changed a lot.

448
00:28:48,270 --> 00:28:49,470
Everything in this world changes

449
00:28:50,670 --> 00:28:51,590
and it changes very fast.

450
00:28:54,230 --> 00:28:55,270
It won't change.

451
00:28:55,990 --> 00:28:57,430
The Yangtze River will always be the Yangtze River.

452
00:28:58,550 --> 00:29:00,310
I'll always be Li Anran.

453
00:29:00,870 --> 00:29:02,510
Won't you always be Liu Wenqin?

454
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:19,230
Just get off here.

455
00:29:20,630 --> 00:29:22,430
Can I still see you in the future?

456
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:45,310
What are you doing here again?

457
00:29:46,710 --> 00:29:48,630
You are no longer a student of this school.

458
00:29:50,470 --> 00:29:51,350
We just can't go back.

459
00:29:55,390 --> 00:29:56,510
Do you hate me so much?

460
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:03,830
She transferred here for you

461
00:30:04,670 --> 00:30:05,430
In order to see you,

462
00:30:05,430 --> 00:30:06,910
she caters for your friends every day.

463
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,390
Why are you so heartless?

464
00:30:14,670 --> 00:30:15,870
They're afraid of you, but I'm not.

465
00:30:17,230 --> 00:30:18,430
Do you know how they fight out there?

466
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,710
What are you going to do?

467
00:30:29,150 --> 00:30:29,763
Leave!

468
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:32,670
Leave!

469
00:30:43,470 --> 00:30:44,070
Get inside!

470
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,163
Everybody get inside!

471
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:51,630
I don't hate you,

472
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:54,910
but I don't want to see you anymore.

473
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:28,630
Such a rascal!

474
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:32,550
Are you sure he's the man you want?

475
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:54,150
Doggo,

476
00:31:55,670 --> 00:31:57,110
why on earth did he do this to me?

477
00:31:59,870 --> 00:32:00,830
My bad, my bad.

478
00:32:02,670 --> 00:32:04,310
He is not good at speech.

479
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:07,150
When he left,

480
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:08,990
he gave me a note

481
00:32:09,190 --> 00:32:10,150
and told me to read it to you.

482
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:11,990
He told me to read it to you.

483
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:26,510
No wonder Liu Wenqin

484
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,630
made me promise

485
00:32:27,630 --> 00:32:29,110
that only I would read it.

486
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:30,630
He said his handwriting was too bad

487
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:31,910
like worms crawling.

488
00:32:31,910 --> 00:32:33,510
Now I see. It is really

489
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:34,590
shameful.

490
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:35,790
What did he write?

491
00:32:39,070 --> 00:32:39,680
Anran.

492
00:32:41,630 --> 00:32:42,430
I'm leaving for a few days.

493
00:32:45,710 --> 00:32:46,990
I'm very happy these days.

494
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:49,550
I can always have lunch with you.

495
00:32:50,430 --> 00:32:52,150
The food you bought is always so delicious.

496
00:32:54,390 --> 00:32:55,270
Sometimes I wonder

497
00:32:56,990 --> 00:32:59,070
if life would stop there forever.

498
00:32:59,910 --> 00:33:01,310
My life is not so wonderful.

499
00:33:03,070 --> 00:33:03,990
Luckily, I've shared

500
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:04,950
some moments with you.

501
00:33:07,910 --> 00:33:08,830
When I come back,

502
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,390
let's have dinner together.

503
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:14,350
Signature.

504
00:33:17,870 --> 00:33:19,910
DOGGO IS AN A-HOLE

505
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:30,713
Liu Wenqin.

506
00:33:35,070 --> 00:33:35,680
Is it true?

507
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:37,750
You see I read it so sincerely.

508
00:33:37,750 --> 00:33:38,510
How could I be lying?

509
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:41,190
I don't care.

510
00:33:41,190 --> 00:33:41,950
I promised Wenqin.

511
00:33:41,990 --> 00:33:43,110
What he said is true.

512
00:33:43,150 --> 00:33:43,910
I bear him out.

513
00:34:05,230 --> 00:34:06,510
You all saw it, didn't you?

514
00:34:08,550 --> 00:34:10,310
Please don't tell her.

515
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,230
Doggo.

516
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:15,470
I didn't expect you to like her so much.

517
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,270
Are you stupid?

518
00:34:20,470 --> 00:34:21,470
Who likes her?

519
00:34:21,550 --> 00:34:23,430
I was just helping my good friend comfort her.

520
00:34:26,350 --> 00:34:28,550
You've suffered too much.

521
00:34:34,710 --> 00:34:35,670
Not at all.

522
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,310
I made it up so seriously.

523
00:34:40,350 --> 00:34:41,670
I almost believed it.

524
00:34:41,790 --> 00:34:43,590
I'm really a talented actor.

525
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:44,830
Doggo.

526
00:34:45,470 --> 00:34:46,080
Let's go.

527
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:48,880
Doggo.

528
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:49,749
Doggo.

529
00:34:55,390 --> 00:34:57,269
Next time you comfort others, don't touch them.

530
00:34:57,669 --> 00:34:58,990
What does it have to do with you?

531
00:35:03,189 --> 00:35:03,796
Hey,

532
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:05,550
let's eat together.

533
00:35:32,269 --> 00:35:33,590
If it were me,

534
00:35:33,749 --> 00:35:35,510
I wouldn't give up the girl I like to others.

535
00:35:37,669 --> 00:35:38,270
What are you talking about?

536
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,470
I'd at least fight for it.

537
00:35:41,310 --> 00:35:42,950
Nothing is impossible.

538
00:35:43,870 --> 00:35:45,630
If my family was as good as yours.

539
00:35:45,950 --> 00:35:47,070
and I were as good as you in all aspects.

540
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,910
I would say the same thing.

541
00:35:51,070 --> 00:35:52,030
But of course,

542
00:35:52,310 --> 00:35:53,550
I'm handsome.

543
00:35:54,830 --> 00:35:55,430
Really!

544
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:57,070
You are really handsome

545
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:58,950
and you're quite nice.

546
00:36:03,670 --> 00:36:05,070
Every cloud has a silver lining,

547
00:36:06,230 --> 00:36:07,710
there's always a way out.

548
00:36:09,870 --> 00:36:10,990
True love

549
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:12,350
will pay off.

550
00:36:13,750 --> 00:36:14,470
What do you mean?

551
00:36:15,310 --> 00:36:15,950
Nothing.

552
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:18,470
I'm actually encouraging myself.

553
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:21,710
Hercules Jiao is as blind as a bat.

554
00:36:22,430 --> 00:36:23,470
That's right.

555
00:36:24,430 --> 00:36:25,670
Anran is the same.

556
00:36:25,950 --> 00:36:27,750
She just completely ignores you

557
00:36:29,350 --> 00:36:31,710
and falls in love with a rascal incomprehensibly.

558
00:36:35,950 --> 00:36:36,910
Oh, women!

559
00:36:43,830 --> 00:36:45,350
When we're seventeen,

560
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:48,110
can we only move ourselves?

561
00:37:09,430 --> 00:37:11,270
Finish this problem before you go.

562
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:19,630
Big Mouth,

563
00:37:19,630 --> 00:37:21,470
do you have any new tricks recently?

564
00:37:21,790 --> 00:37:23,190
How can I have so many tricks?

565
00:37:23,390 --> 00:37:24,510
Do you have to make a big sensation every time?

566
00:37:24,990 --> 00:37:25,790
Right.

567
00:37:25,790 --> 00:37:26,750
Let me tell you something.

568
00:37:26,750 --> 00:37:28,030
If you really like someone,

569
00:37:28,070 --> 00:37:29,870
just tell her sincerely.

570
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:31,750
Playing so many tricks.

571
00:37:31,790 --> 00:37:32,870
What's the use of that?

572
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:02,710
Dear Wenqin,

573
00:38:02,750 --> 00:38:04,790
I think we should drink more today.

574
00:38:04,870 --> 00:38:06,030
For what?

575
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:12,390
Girl, you've been sitting here for half an hour.

576
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:13,550
It's a small business.

577
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:14,590
Please order something.

578
00:38:18,070 --> 00:38:18,790
Chicken...

579
00:38:20,750 --> 00:38:21,430
wings!

580
00:38:25,830 --> 00:38:26,550
Chicken...

581
00:38:27,870 --> 00:38:28,670
legs!

582
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:31,910
Who is this girl?

583
00:38:33,350 --> 00:38:34,350
And chicken...

584
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:36,430
feet!

